\begin_inset Formula $n\neq0$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

: 
\begin_inset Formula $\mbox{char}(K)=0$
\end_inset

, or 
\begin_inset Formula $\mbox{char}(K)=p$
\end_inset

