\begin_inset Formula $K(\mu_{n})$
\end_inset

: adjoining one primitive 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

th root of unity is the same as adjoining a ful set of 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

th roots of unity.
 
